    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Animated wolf corpses with empty, milky eye sockets, blind draugr wolves navigate the frozen Bone-Fields entirely by sound and scent. Matted frost-rimed fur clings to skeletal frames that move with coordinated, pack precision. They hunt in groups of six, immune to darkness, illusions, or any concealment based on sight. Their Frenzy Snap leaves targets vulnerable — perfect setup for the Dire Draugr Wolf that commands them.</p>",
